          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".The cross sections at forward angles 7-40",
                "degrees were measured by a delta E-E telescope",
                "consisting of semiconductor detectors. The thickness",
                "of E-counter was 600 mum and delta-E counters was",
                " 25 mum.",
                "For the measurements in the medium angular range",
                " (Ang=40-80 degree) a position-sensitive delta-E-E",
                "detector was used with delta-E as a gas-filled",
                "proportional counter and a E-detector consisting of ten",
                "silicon pin-diodes of 10*10 mm dimension each and",
                "thickness of 380-760 mum.",
                "The scattering events at large angles (Ang=80-130",
                "degree) were measured using kinematical coincidences-",
                "two silicon detectors of the sizes 30*30 mm and",
                " 100*10 mm were (in the latter case the position-",
                "sensitive detector mentioned above was used without its",
                "delta-E part) were located on the both sides of the",
                "beam, at distances of 600 mm and 300 mm from the",
                "target, respectively."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
